quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  77,20,"Mbela Min tagaani mon- onon aade en-ummaade e ndiyam kou…óam ko …óaam woni to…ì…ìere maniyyu."
  77,21,"Min mba…ói ndiyam …óam e nokku deenaa…óo ko oon woni rannga debba."
  77,22,"Haa e dumunna ganndaa…óo ko oon woni yonto caawgol suko."
  77,23,"Min koddiri sifa jibinaa…óo o mbaadi makko e ko nanndi heen, heskey Oon koddir…óo …óuum fof Minen."
  77,24,"Halkaare e lepte e perte woodanii wonande …ìeen fennoo…ìe baawal Alla."
  77,25,"Mbela Min mba…óaani leydi ndi na sooma aade en fof."
  77,26,"Hondi renndini won…ìe heen wuur…ìe e maay…ìe ubbaa…ìe e hendi ."
  77,27,"Min mba…ói e hendi pelle tabit…óe, na ndeena ndi e dillude toow…óe, Min njarndi mon ndiyam mbel…óam, tag…óo …óuum horataaka umminde mon."
  77,28,"Halkaare e lepte woodanii wonande …ìeen fennoo…ìe njo…ìdi mum en √±ande √±alngu jnobdi."
  77,29,"Wiyanee fennoo…ìe ko nelaa…ìe ngaddi ko- onon fennoobe- kuu∆¥e faade ko pennatna…óon ko e lepte."
  77,30,"Njahee faade e mbeelu cuurki yiit mbanndi cate tate."
  77,31,"∆Åuu…ìol …óowdi alah toon, ndi ha…óatah lew lewndu yiite e nguli mum yande e mon."
  77,32,"Yiite nge na werlo peete, kala heen wootere Alla no mawniri a sikkat ko hu…ìeere."
  77,33,"Peete werletee…óe Alla no…óe …ìalwiri e no…óe mawniri a sikkat ko…óe geloobi …ìaleeji."
  77,34,"Halkaare woodanii wonande …ìeen fennoo…ìe njo…ìdi mum en √±ande √±alngu jnobdi."
  77,35,"E o √±alngu …ìe kaalatah hay huunde."
  77,36,"∆Åe cakkitantaake sabu …ìe ngantina faade e joom mum en ko faati e keefeeru e bone mum en, …ìe …óa…ì…ìira Mbo ngantu."
  77,37,"Halkaare e perte woodanii …ìeen fennoo…ìe kabaruuji √±alngu jnobdi."
  77,38,"O ko √±alngu ceerndugol hakkunde tagaa…óe, Min ndenndinii on e le∆¥∆¥i gadii…ói e dingiral gootal."
  77,39,"Si tawii ho…óon nda√±i feere nde puuntiraton haa nda…óon e lepte Alla pewjanee lan."
  77,40,"Halkaare woodanii wonande …ìeen fennoo…ìe njo…ìdi mum en √±ande √±alngu jno…ìdi."
  77,41,"Pellet …ìeen reentirii…ìe joom mum siinude jamirooje Alla e reentaade ka…óe Makko, ho…ìe e nder …óowdi lek…óe aljanna e ceewle ndiyam bel…óe ilooje."
  77,42,"E …ìesnaa…óe …óe…ìe tuuyate √±aamde."
  77,43,"∆Åe wi*anee:√±aame e laa…ì…ói, njaron njaram mbel…óam …óam alah lorla, sabu ko golle mon mo∆¥∆¥e ka aduna."
  77,44,"Yeru ndi njo…ìdi ndi Min njo…ìi mon, ko hono ndi Min njo…ìirta labin…ìe golle mum en."
  77,45,"Halkaare e lepte e perte woodanii …ìeen fennoo…ìe ko Alla heblani hul…ìe e jno…ìdi."
  77,46,"Fennu…ìe …ìe na wiyee:√±aame ndakmita…óon e wela wela nguurndam tuma setta ka aduna, ko on bon…ìe sabu ko pennu…óon ko Alla e nelaa…ìe Makko."
  77,47,"Halkaare woodanii wonande …ìeen fennoo…ìe njo…ìdi mum en √±ande √±alngu jno…ìdi."
  77,48,"Si …ìee fennoo…ìe mbiyaama: njuule ngam Alla …ìe njuulatah."
  77,49,"Halkaare e lepte e perte e oon √±alawma woodanii fennu…ìe ko nelaa…ìe ngaddi ko ummaade ka Alla."
  77,50,"Si…ìe goon…óinaani oo Quraana tellinaa…óo ummaade ka Alla honde yeewtere wo…ónde …ìe goon…óinta?."